, 102.4319, 101.4199, 100.3138, 99.825, 99.8657, 98.6414, 98.1602, 96.9551, 97.022, 97.5061, 97.5293, 96.5359, 95.8583, 95.7404, 96.8485, 96.871, 96.9781, 96.9461, 96.8193, 97.3577, 98.397, 97.9118, 97.8354, 96.6267, 95.5059, 94.9413, 93.8405, 93.7495, 94.6647, 94.1976, 94.7579, 94.3924, 93.2837, 92.8541, 93.0931, 94.2886, 94.8506, 94.0786, 93.9421, 94.0985, 93.7893, 93.319, 92.1182, 91.0379, 91.2469, 89.8258, 90.0623, 86.7703, 85.4111, 86.9494, 85.8626, 85.2653, 84.2569, 83.8499, 82.7304, 83.4659, 83.1923, 84.2237, 84.6694, 85.2694, 84.2067, 85.1034, 84.4881, 84.6968, 82.0245, 80.6924, 79.6523, 79.4145, 78.6122, 77.5807, 77.7432, 76.6746, 77.4003, 76.7398, 76.6068, 77.1423, 76.808, 75.1482, 75.646, 75.5051, 74.4077, 74.639, 74.8502, 76.3343, 75.4426, 74.6735, 75.5105, 73.8944, 72.8519, 72.7799, 72.6008, 72.178, 71.0081, 67.5551, 63.3643, 64.4134, 65.5726, 65.7883, 66.2221, 67.0258, 68.7063, 67.6883, 65.6014, 65.3038, 63.7606, 62.6472, 63.4773, 61.2754, 63.265, 63.4617, 63.1162, 63.1778, 61.8834, 62.5631, 62.619, 62.9278, 62.5379, 62.5293, 62.4797, 62.5149, 61.9134, 61.9465, 62.3731, 64.1581, 63.3265, 64.6752, 63.7573, 63.8784, 65.4018, 65.693, 66.2362, 64.7626, 64.2387, 64.5258, 65.094, 65.1459, 65.2853, 66.6993, 66.9676, 66.7439, 68.8127, 67.8956, 67.9573, 69.2115, 70.4427, 71.4054, 71.4735, 70.2029, 68.9553, 69.565, 69.1206, 69.2968, 66.6024, 65.2126, 65.636, 63.5069, 62.0181, 63.396, 64.2561, 61.1174, 61.0268, 60.4036, 61.2623, 64.6781, 64.1073, 62.6124, 62.0368, 62.6967, 63.1057, 62.4141, 61.2733, 61.136, 60.1221, 62.4222, 63.8216, 63.0171, 62.3823, 63.1725, 61.9982, 61.7814, 61.5286, 60.378, 60.8752, 60.5588, 60.6141, 59.8598, 58.765, 60.1563, 62.6799, 64.325, 64.3429, 64.3405, 66.6885, 69.0978, 65.7062, 70.7522, 72.2217, 72.8724, 72.642, 73.2311, 74.6816, 71.2809, 69.7369, 70.1677, 70.1923], "summary_html": "<h1>蜘蛛网策略：基于席位持仓变动的截面因子</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原始策略基于股指期货前20大结算会员的多空持仓增量(dB, dS)构建交易信号：当多头增仓且空头减仓时做多，反之做空。本复现将其泛化为商品期货截面因子：使用 <code>memberdiff20</code>（前20名席位净持仓差）经 OPI 归一化后的 5 日变化，做截面排名得到多空信号。核心逻辑是：机构席位的相对持仓变动反映了知情交易者(informed trader)的方向判断，在商品期货中同样具有预测意义。OPI 归一化使不同品种间的信号具有可比性，截面排名进一步消除了品种间量纲差异。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.14</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>0.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-13.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.14</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1754</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.52</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-2.67</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.48 / 0.55</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.88</td><td>0.59</td><td>0.06</td><td>1.97</td><td>0.06</td><td>0.69</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.57</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.44</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1750</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>97.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>48.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>核心信号计算：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{md20\\_ratio}_t^i = \\frac{\\text{memberdiff20}_t^i}{\\text{OPI}_t^i}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\Delta_5 = \\text{md20\\_ratio}_t^i - \\text{md20\\_ratio}_{t-5}^i</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_t^i = \\text{CrossSectionalPercentileRank}(\\Delta_5)</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t^i = 2 \\times (\\text{rank}_t^i - 0.5) \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_t^i = \\text{signal}_t^i \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_t^i \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{memberdiff20}_t^i</span>：品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日前20大席位净持仓差（多头持仓 - 空头持仓）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{OPI}_t^i</span>：品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日的总持仓量</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\Delta_5</span>：5日归一化持仓变动</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{\\text{target}} = 0.15</span>：年化波动率目标</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat{\\sigma}_t^i</span>：60日滚动已实现波动率</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.34, 换手率 4.03 极高, 信号方向频繁翻转</td><td>1日变化+moi组合, persistent_signal+rebalance_hold(5)</td><td>combo_md20_moi 最优 0.34, 信号太噪</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>Sharpe 0.58, 换手率降至 2.39, 但信号衰减严重(前半2.08/后半-0.08)</td><td>改用截面排名(rank)而非方向信号, 更长平滑窗口(MA5/10/20), hold=10/20</td><td>rank_ma5_h10 最优 0.58, 截面方法更稳定但衰减未解</td></tr><tr><td><strong>R3</strong></td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>: 引入 OPI 归一化的 memberdiff20 比率</td><td>memberdiff20/OPI 的 5日变化做截面排名, hold=10</td><td><strong>rank_rr5_h10 达 1.09</strong>, 半样本从不平衡(2.08/-0.08)变为稳定(1.57/1.42)</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R3 将 memberdiff20 除以 OPI 进行归一化后，消除了不同品种持仓量级差异的干扰，使截面排名更具可比性。这是 Sharpe 从 0.58 跳升至 1.09 且信号稳定性大幅改善的核心原因。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部 57 个商品期货品种（有 memberdiff20 数据的品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10 天换仓</li>\n<li><strong>数据非空率</strong>: memberdiff20 约 25%，自 2018 年底起数据较为完整</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - memberdiff20 数据覆盖从 2018 年底开始，有效回测区间约 6 年\n<p>- 部分品种席位数据质量参差不齐，可能存在噪声 - 原始策略针对股指期货(IF)，泛化到商品期货后信号逻辑有所调整 - 2025 年年度 Sharpe 略为负值(-0.10)，需持续监控</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.11s</li>\n</ul>"}